	(197, 1, '2014-03-14 13:15:03', '2014-03-14 13:15:03', '[spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3" el_position="first"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tshirts.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">T-SHIRTS</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£25 - £70</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The staple element of a man\'s wardrobe. We\'ve got tees, polo\'s, v-necks, crew-necks. All your basic needs.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/shirts.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000;">SHIRTS</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£60 - £100</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Formal, casual Friday, linens for holidays, a well fitted button up shirt is an essential. Casual or smart - we have it.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3" el_position="last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="http://enclothed.dev/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/blazers.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000;">BLAZERS</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£85 - £250</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Very few items are as sophisticated yet versatile as a blazer. Casual fabric to smart tailored, we have types for any occasion.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_parallax parallax_type="image" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" alt_background="none" el_class="grey_bg area3" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000; line-height: 34px;">WHEN DO I PAY</span></p>\r\n<img class="size-full aligncenter" alt="line" src="/wp-content/themes/dante-child/images/line.png" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ever heard of try then buy? You enter your credit card details when you order a box but you don\'t pay until you\'ve received it all and decided what you want to keep.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Once your box has arrived you have 10 days to try everything on. What you like you keep. What you don\'t we collect. We will only charge you for what you keep.</p>\r\n[/spb_parallax] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3" el_position="first"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/jackets.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">JACKETS</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£75 - £200</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The right jacket can change an outfit entirely. From suede to hooded, we\'ve got it all.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/trousers.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">TROUSERS</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£80 - £170</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Chinos, jeans, cords, or formal - our trouser collection will be sure to get you noticed.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3" el_position="last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/knitware.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">KNITWARE</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£50 - £120</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Keeping you warm during Winter through to the chill of Spring. We carry many types to keep you covered.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_parallax parallax_type="image" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" alt_background="none" el_class="grey_bg area5" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000; line-height: 34px;">WHAT WILL ARRIVE IN MY BOX?</span></p>\r\n<img class="size-full aligncenter" alt="line" src="/wp-content/themes/dante-child/images/line.png" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">You will typically receive 6-10 items in your box consisting of 3 out-of-the-box outfits. 1 or 2 pairs of trousers, a shirt, t-shirt, polo, a pair of shoes and a blazer. You can also specifically ask for certain items or tell us if there\'s something that you don\'t want.. you\'re the boss.</p>\r\n[/spb_parallax] [spb_column width="1/6" el_position="first"] [/spb_column] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/shoes.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">SHOES</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£65 - £200</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">"It\'s his shoes I notice first" - make sure you\'ve got the right ones on.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/assesories.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">ACCESSSORIES</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #b08536;">£12 - £170</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Glasses, tech cases, belts, pocket squares - all the finishing touches.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_column width="1/6" el_position="last"] [/spb_column] [spb_parallax parallax_type="image" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" alt_background="none" el_class="grey_bg area7" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 34px;">HOW MUCH WOULD YOU TYPICALLY SPEND ON EACH ITEM?</p>\r\n<img class="size-full aligncenter" alt="line" src="/wp-content/themes/dante-child/images/line.png" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We work closely with you to understand your budget for each item in your box and you will only pay the same as you would in the shops. You only pay for what you keep – no added costs. Deliveries and collections are on us.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We work with great brands that provide excellent quality that you can wear time and time again. These brands will become an essential part of your wardrobe and are brands that you will find in high-end department stores.</p>\r\n[/spb_parallax]', 'Pricing', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pricing', '', '', '2014-04-09 14:12:28', '2014-04-09 14:12:28', '', 0, 'http://enclothed.dev/?page_id=197', 0, 'page', '', 0),
