ail price on the\r\nclothes. You are only charged after the 10 day trying on period, once\r\neverything is back at Enclothed HQ and we see what has been kept.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_parallax parallax_type="image" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" alt_background="none" el_class="area_gold" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #fff; font-family: Georgia; font-style: italic; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0;">Free deliveries and collections</span>[sf_button colour="blue" type="standard" size="standard" link="#" icon="ss-erase" dropshadow="no" extraclass="login_link"]<span style="color: #ffffff;">MORE DETAILS</span>[/sf_button]</p>\r\n[/spb_parallax]', 'How it works', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-01 12:06:14', '2014-04-01 12:06:14', '', 8, 'http://enclothed.dev/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
