	(811, 2, '2014-01-26 09:42:07', '2014-01-26 17:42:07', '<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/67141f6a91fa9dfdedf48c25be40e853/tumblr_inline_n00p9aJpuH1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>Show-stopping patterns were a trend that appeared across the board at London Collections earlier this month.</p>\n<p>Prints are going to be bolder than ever this year. Check, geometric and stripes are going to be wardrobe essentials. Need some inspiration? Here’s how they look on the catwalk and how you can team other items in your wardrobe with prints.</p>\n<p><strong>Checks on the runway:</strong></p>\n<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/74069d05e24a2c8e16e9c4277a009ea1/tumblr_inline_n00qhm9vle1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>Hackett, E.Tautz, Oliver Spencer | Source: londoncollections.co.uk</p>\n<p><strong>How to wear it:</strong></p>\n<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/c940714137db4367c3f93284760f08d4/tumblr_inline_n00qlceQO01rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p><strong>Geometric print on the runway: </strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/19ba926d1a7db84e811d67a84b6dee88/tumblr_inline_n00rdgDWBs1rd6zrs.jpg"/></strong></p>\n<p>Burberry Prorsum, John Smedley, Nicole Farhi | Source: londoncollections.co.uk</p>\n<p><strong>How to wear it:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/f3c458c07350d1438c3b077f96a6923d/tumblr_inline_n00rezmJqA1rd6zrs.jpg"/></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Stripes on the runway:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/4ce06a50e1a3cf2440057e647debb16a/tumblr_inline_n00rnzR6MS1rd6zrs.jpg"/></strong></p>\n\n<p>Jonathan Saunders, Casely-Hayford, E. Tautz | Source: londoncollections.co.uk</p>\n<p><strong>How to wear it:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/f8e75ac06663b27bef031c78b2195871/tumblr_inline_n00rrnTluv1rd6zrs.jpg"/></strong></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '811', '', '', '2014-01-26 09:42:07', '2014-01-26 17:42:07', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/7462