	(812, 2, '2014-01-23 07:47:09', '2014-01-23 15:47:09', '<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/f5eec559c86286a753f6024a70559f30/tumblr_inline_mzv2ctWEbW1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>With winter here, its time to start layering and the cardigan is one item that is well worth a place in your wardrobe.</p>\n<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/6b06d2fa467e302327029749b98c1363/tumblr_inline_mzv2c1vPnv1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p><strong>Why?</strong></p>\n<p>The cardigan is a master of versatility. Worn alone a cardigan can be an excellent substitute to a Blazer or sports coat and with chillier conditions approaching they can be the perfect layering piece under a jacket providing needed warm and insulation. They can be dressed up or dressed down a staple item you can wear again and again making it great value for money.</p>\n<p><strong>What type of cardigan?</strong> </p>\n<p>This really is up to you.  When going for a winter warmer try a cardigan with a heavy wool knit, which will provide added warmth. Make sure you are going to be comfortable wearing it; give the wool a feel anything too scratchy will mean that you need a long sleeve layer underneath. Merino wool is usually more comfortable on the skin, although it is more expensive.</p>\n<p>Wool cardigans usually can’t be machined washed and are better hand washed or dry-cleaned so keep that in mind also.</p>\n<p>For a cardigan, which can be dressed up, premium fibres such as cashmere are warm and light.  They are a considerable investment into you wardrobe so make sure to go for a timeless, dark or neutral tone.</p>\n<p>You can then get 10+ years wear out of it if looked after properly - so protect your investment and hand wash exclusively.</p>\n<p><strong>Fit</strong></p>\n<p>Ultimately you need to make sure your cardigan fits.  Avoid a cardigan that is too tight but make sure that is tapers at the waist and falls loosely over your belt buckle but not long enough to cover your pockets. The shoulder seams should end on the top of your shoulder and it should not be loose giving you a pouch every time you lean forward. </p>\n<p>Finally to button or unbutton – the rule of thumb is always leave the bottom button undone this will help avoid the front pouch mentioned but other than that experiment with rest as much as you like.</p>\n<p>Last of all don’t let anyone tell you cardigans are not manly. Named after the 7th Earl of Cardigan, the first British officer to cross the Russian lines in the famous Charge of the Light Brigade, during the Crimean war what can be manlier than that! </p>\n<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/1cc2024af9eedc57fc2aea8c1ade2b89/tumblr_inline_mzv2exh4bO1rd6zrs.png"/></p>\n\n<p>Picture source: Gant.co.uk</p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '812', '', '', '2014-01-23 07:47:09', '2014-01-23 15:47:09', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/74282922032', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(813, 2, '2014-01-21 11:02:00', '2014-01-21 19:02:00', '<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/4fee77355de2fa971287914bd9c020d7/tumblr_inline_mzrkvaxqgv1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>London Collections: Men. We saw some great Catwalk shows, decadent showrooms and fantastic presentations.</p>\n<p>One hot topic between Enclothed stylist and their customers is how to translate the catwalk to everyday wear. One trend that consistently appears in Winter is fur and faux fur, as seen on the runways of Christopher Raeburn, Sibling, Astrid and Hackett. Of course you don’t need to go all out to wear fur this season</p>\n<p><strong>Catwalk look:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/eabcf3372c5b4fa69941868d4bae16be/tumblr_inline_mzrlf5gsLQ1rd6zrs.jpg"/></strong></p>\n\n<p>Christopher Raeburn and Astrid AW14 | Source: londoncollections.co.uk</p>\n<p>Buying pieces with fur details will add a stylish subtle touch to your look and still keep you on trend. Christopher Raeburn and Hackett’s models wore thick warm fur hooded coats, a look we expect to be seeing a lot more of on the high street this year. Sibling’s take on fur was slightly different, showing some amazing snug jumpers with fur collars. </p>\n<p>Everyday wear:</p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/9ccd866147b07f6aa8d6a34c5993e898/tumblr_inline_mzrlyiu8s41rd6zrs.jpg"/>Christopher Raeburn, Hackett, Sibling | Source: londoncollections.co.uk</p>\n<p>A great brand that has already tapped into this trend is Parka London - A London based debut brand dedicated to timeless designs, high quality garments and special details which are the brand’s signature design. Such details include detachable fur hoods, luxe linings, secret drawstrings and distinctive silhouettes. <a href="http://www.parkalondon.com">http://www.parkalondon.com</a></p>\n<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/67b4c35dde24134ad88f8d570ab84f6b/tumblr_inline_mzrmb9aOp11rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '813', '', '', '2014-01-21 11:02:00', '2014-01-21 19:02:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/74082165626', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(814, 2, '2014-01-17 09:02:00', '2014-01-17 17:02:00', '<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/40f5bb52b4a28d48d9feb1ffc0bc411d/tumblr_inline_mzk0klOas51rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/c5cc53b17ebcfd7940e039dc22c73b45/tumblr_inline_mzjzv5dusj1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/cfdff4eaf040e20503cca127b6954605/tumblr_inline_mzjzzcvgow1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p> Dana Zingher, Paul Mckenna, Terry O’Neil, Paul Young, Levi Young </p>\n<p>The private viewing of  ‘The Best of Terry O’Neil’ at The Little Black Gallery was a great success. We were thrilled to be part of the celebration of such an iconic photographer. Here are a few of the stylish guests that attended the event.</p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/c37b6b11f9205891d6c6748e63c5c02a/tumblr_inline_mzk0orcEZy1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p>     Terry O’Neil                                Paul Young                             Barry Vera</p>\n\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/d0c7b3214330ace40629d5f6e53d25b0/tumblr_inline_mzk17vpN2S1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>                                                                Paul Keenan</p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/7f121e8ada4bcf6336f929db7f90465e/tumblr_inline_mzk1nhTARC1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/4b08b827ae5e5561aeec2d0720f13a3a/tumblr_inline_mzk1ptMBUf1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>Melissa Odabash, Tamara Beckwith, Kelly Hoppen, Natasha Corrett</p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/f8f734801eb257411f2b08952292c443/tumblr_inline_mzk1rzAkiD1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>It was a delightful evening!</p>\n<p>Curious to learn more about Mr O’Neil’s incredible work? Getty Images made a great interview with the British legend:</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3MRhz36adfU">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3MRhz36adfU</a></p>\n<p>The Little Black Gallery will be hosting his pieces for the next two weeks so be sure to head down to view the very best of Terry O’Neill. More information at <a href="http://www.thelittleblackgallery.com">http://www.thelittleblackgallery.com</a></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '814', '', '', '2014-01-17 09:02:00', '2014-01-17 17:02:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/73624319880', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(815, 2, '2014-01-16 06:02:00', '2014-01-16 14:02:00', '<p class="p1"><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/f556caf120d7983f5829b74363a0574e/tumblr_inline_mzhzd7Agjy1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p class="p1"></p>\n<p class="p1">Enclothed are pleased to be sponsoring this evenings private <span class="s1">viewing</span> of  ‘The Best of Terry O&#8217;Neil’ at The Little Black Gallery. Terry <span class="s2">O&#8217;Neil</span> made his name <span class="s3">documenting the fashions, styles, and celebrities of the 1960&#8217;s. </span></p>\n<p class="p3">No other living photographer has captured such an array of icons throughout the ages, such as Winston Churchill, Nelson Mandella, Frank Sinatra, Elvis Presley, Audrey Hepburn, Brigitte Bardot to Amy Winehouse and Nicole Kidman, as well as every James Bond from Sean Connery to Pierce Brosnan - to name a few!</p>\n<p class="p1">One of our favourites from the exhibition is this photograph of Frank Sinatra from 1968.  </p>\n<p class="p5"><span class="s4"><a href="http://www.thelittleblackgallery.com/">www.thelittleblackgallery.com</a></span></p>\n\n<p class="p5"><span class="s4"><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/3dfcc53ef6ad6a8a52c29cec1e203d75/tumblr_inline_mzhyw4VeSa1rd6zrs.jpg"/></span></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '815', '', '', '2014-01-16 06:02:00', '2014-01-16 14:02:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/73510792747', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(816, 2, '2014-01-14 04:47:00', '2014-01-14 12:47:00', '<p><span class="s1"><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/2239dbf84d9e8a22f811ce67b20dd548/tumblr_inline_mze5vuV23r1rd6zrs.jpg"/><span class="s1">A </span><span>Harrington is a lightweight waist-length jacket often with a checked or tartan lining. It has been an iconic piece of british fashion since the 1930&#8217;s. </span></span></p>\n<p class="p2">Our favourites include this G4 Original in cream with a classic tartan lining from Baracuta <span class="s4">and this Gant </span><span>Harrington. We love the contemporary twist of the check print on the outside! </span></p>\n<p class="p2"><span><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/4f5cd3a882a2dd3a45a4239ed20f8779/tumblr_inline_mze568oZKA1rd6zrs.jpg"/></span></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '816', '', '', '2014-01-14 04:47:00', '2014-01-14 12:47:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/73301539693', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(817, 2, '2014-01-07 03:02:00', '2014-01-07 11:02:00', '<p class="p1"><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/952333d8cd83f618e2891d0f8124d187/tumblr_inline_mz12keYPeC1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p class="p1"><span><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/b4935ee39af86fc2303f6cf723bcfff0/tumblr_inline_mz12u0jgad1rd6zrs.jpg"/></span></p>\n<p class="p1"><span>Can you wear smart trainers with chinos? One simple answer YES! David Beckham and his boys rock the chino trainer combo well and Adidas are so convinced of this stylish pairing they have bought out their own line of Chinos!</span></p>\n<p class="p1"><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/959055733d935fe4189edb88fd7f0a37/tumblr_inline_mz11tr8UjY1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p class="p1">(Image source prodirectselect.com)</p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '817', '', '', '2014-01-07 03:02:00', '2014-01-07 11:02:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/72543720310', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(818, 2, '2014-01-02 03:31:40', '2014-01-02 11:31:40', '<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/26a7d8e48d0b579d80c0fcb910f31785/tumblr_inline_myruku8saE1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p class="p1">Eddie Redmayne caught our attention with both his casual and tailored styles. <span class="s1">Eddie is going from strength to strength and is set to make waves in 2014. </span></p>\n<p class="p3">Our Stylist says: This is a great example of how to layer this winter. Eddie is wearing a stylish high street suit from Topman with an olive green button down cardigan over a chocolate brown shirt. </p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '818', '', '', '2014-01-02 03:31:40', '2014-01-02 11:31:40', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/71956215441', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(819, 2, '2013-12-26 03:52:05', '2013-12-26 11:52:05', '<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/0ed8d78e02e88c03533fd0a89674aa7c/tumblr_inline_myewiv7AcI1rd6zrs.jpg"/>Yes! Here are three examples of when you can put them to great use.</p>\n<p><strong>1. Work.</strong> The office no longer stays in the office. Laptop, mobile phone, paper work and contracts all frequently come home with us. The traditional brief case is looking a bit dated with even the governor the Bank of England, Mark Carney, carrying a man bag instead so who are we to argue.</p>\n<p>Our favourite being this Maxwell Scott. Simple, classic and practical.</p>\n<p><br/><strong>2. Sport.</strong> Be it popping to the gym after work, football training or tennis, every man needs a good sports bag. Gone are the days of the funny little P.E bags. Now there are a range of stylish mens sports bags that don&#8217;t make you look like a teen.</p>\n<p>For a more sophisticated bag that can take you from work to the gym, try a weekend bag such as this Hugo Boss Weekender.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Every Day.</strong> A book to read on the train, a bottle of water, wallet, house keys and all those other little bits you end up carrying around in your pockets making your clothes look lumpy and bumpy can now be slipped into a stylish messenger bag.</p>\n<p>Who can resist this Italian hide leather messenger bag with embossed dog from Tyler and Tyler. </p>\n<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/62c52d0186a34b86249f9681ae17f7f3/tumblr_inline_myewusdVs91rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '819', '', '', '2013-12-26 03:52:05', '2013-12-26 11:52:05', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/71195120080', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(820, 2, '2013-12-24 04:16:07', '2013-12-24 12:16:07', '<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/ccf5d55c226a5b351122ca43bbd957f4/tumblr_inline_myb8oqo7oY1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p><strong>Rule 1) Wear a dark pair of chinos</strong></p>\n<p>Chino&#8217;s are smarter and more comfortable than jeans. Make sure they are dark enough to withstand spilt wine or food.</p>\n<p><strong>Rule 2) Wear a casual, non-crease shirt &amp; jumper combination</strong></p>\n<p>The great thing about this look is that once you take the jumper off and you have a whole different outfit.</p>\n<p><strong>Rule 3) Peacoat</strong></p>\n<p>Peacoat’s are extremely versatile. With the jumper this coat looks casual or with just the shirt it&#8217;s smart. Best of all it&#8217;s warm so will keep you alive at 3am</p>\n<p><strong>Rule 4) No suede</strong></p>\n<p>Mulled wine, pie, rain&#8230; if you are not careful you will be looking like Fagin in no time.</p>\n<p><strong>Rule 5) Have some coffee!</strong></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '820', '', '', '2013-12-24 04:16:07', '2013-12-24 12:16:07', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/71000889019', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(821, 2, '2013-12-22 07:44:00', '2013-12-22 15:44:00', '<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/bea66eab139983127f35fd734dd237d1/tumblr_inline_my7u73P74Y1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>Christmas jumpers became popular during the 1980s after various T.V presenters began wearing them during the holiday season. Over time their popularity has grown, with most retailers delivering a stylish version or two in their winter collections. Here are a few of our favourites. </p>\n\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/8e0d1afe6f35374abd2dbe9a30b320fe/tumblr_inline_my7sxuXepg1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>Our stylist Layla says: Our top pick is jumper number 4. This Tommy Hilfiger pure cotton kyle knit jumper has a playful element without compromising on style. Perfect for Christmas Day! </p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '821', '', '', '2013-12-22 07:44:00', '2013-12-22 15:44:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/70791476521', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(822, 2, '2013-12-19 06:23:58', '2013-12-19 14:23:58', '<p><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/20693f9676db7c8b2596f007a29d5541/tumblr_inline_my25a7nsVT1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p></p>\n<p class="p1"><strong>Trains&#8230;</strong></p>\n<p class="p2">The perfect garment for long cold train journeys has to be this Gant wool double-breasted officers coat with impressive leather accents on the sleeve and pockets, and contrasting corduroy collar. Suave, sophisticated and really, really warm!</p>\n<p class="p2"><strong>Planes&#8230;</strong></p>\n<p class="p2">This super soft Sunspel 100% cashmere grey Buchanan scarf comes highly recommended for your winter wardrobe. AS well as making you look great and feel warm this scarf will also fold up to be a perfect little pillow. </p>\n<p class="p2"><strong>Automobiles…</strong></p>\n<p class="p2">Scraping frost from the windscreen never looked so stylish thanks to these Dents Men&#8217;s deerskin leather driving gloves with removable cashmere lining. </p>\n\n<p class="p2"><img src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/9d6a3c160da1f73156ff282308c9124a/tumblr_inline_my2559MN2t1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '822', '', '', '2013-12-19 06:23:58', '2013-12-19 14:23:58', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/70488336384', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(823, 2, '2013-12-13 09:01:00', '2013-12-13 17:01:00', '<p><img alt="image" src="https://31.media.tumblr.com/39f7aa7490c569b48a9d4bdb359a0449/tumblr_inline_mxr8kqzPxG1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>Your loved ones will never guess you left it last minute with gifts like these! Best of all you don&#8217;t even have to leave the house to order them.</p>\n<p><strong>For the foodie</strong>: Hello Fresh is a great concept for those who want to discover the joy of cooking! They provide you with recipe cards, pictures, all the ingredients you need – already measured out ready for you to make a delicious dish all delivered to your door. <a href="http://www.hellofresh.co.uk" title="www.hellofresh.co.uk">www.hellofresh.co.uk </a></p>\n<p><strong>For the beauty lover</strong>: This is a great way to discover the most coveted beauty products, beautifully wrapped in the signature pink box and delivered straight to your door each month. <a href="http://www.glossybox.co.uk" title="www.glossybox.co.uk">www.glossybox.co.uk</a></p>\n<p><strong>For the healthy one</strong>: Graze is a brilliant delivery service. Healthy foods that actually taste good, handpicked and delivered your home or office. <a href="http://www.graze.com" title="www.graze.com">www.graze.com</a></p>', 'GIFTS FOR YOUR LOVED ONES', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gifts-for-your-loved-ones', '', '', '2013-12-13 09:01:00', '2013-12-13 17:01:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/69890205965', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(824, 2, '2013-10-30 06:48:43', '2013-10-30 13:48:43', '<p><a href="http://bainser.com/post/65039071425/enclothed-exclusive-styling-menswear" title="Bainser Press"><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/1777e2d4b977ffc2863267163a7ce1fc/tumblr_inline_mvhicmx0HB1rd6zrs.png"/></a></p>', 'Bainser reviews Enclothed ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bainser-reviews-enclothed', '', '', '2013-10-30 06:48:43', '2013-10-30 13:48:43', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/65522085945', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(825, 2, '2013-10-02 04:39:08', '2013-10-02 11:39:08', '<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/fb9d7f1d87bd0070671d1b9fba126614/tumblr_inline_mu1gbxfMqH1rd6zrs.png"/></p>\n\n<p>Every day we get asked style questions from our customers that our stylists love to answer. So we&#8217;ve decided to open it up to non-members too. Every week we&#8217;ll be posting our top style question and answer. To get involved simply tweet your question to @enclothed followed by #stylesession.</p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/697c3834207895a673744f9c71cdb16f/tumblr_inline_mu1ghkvtrp1rd6zrs.png"/></p>\n<p>Dark colours are the perfect contrast. When wearing a navy suit a sharp dark brown brogue will actually enhance the blue in a navy suit more than a black shoe can. </p>\n<p>                         <img src="http://media.tumblr.com/44f4a327c713075f665ea181831b0cc4/tumblr_inline_mu1hkpVIvS1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p>Brown is also more versatile as it can be worn with any colour (apart from black).</p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '825', '', '', '2013-10-02 04:39:08', '2013-10-02 11:39:08', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/62893672062', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(826, 2, '2013-08-02 08:16:15', '2013-08-02 15:16:15', '<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/4acf3c8951c0ea625613893086cd36bf/tumblr_inline_mqwrvsj1C11qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p></p>\n<p>A recent survey by YouGov has concluded that bright red trousers are a faux pax. Here at Enclothed we tend to disagree.</p>\n\n<p>Our stylists have chosen their favourite ways to work the red chino.</p>\n\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/889a2cefee7312d905b070c8d970a696/tumblr_inline_mqwrwkRPrr1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p></p>\n<p>Layla:</p>\n<p>"Wear it with a blazer and t-shirt or shirt and cardigan, you can&#8217;t go wrong"</p>\n\n<p>Raquel:</p>\n<p>"When I think red chino, I think geek chic - a knitted tie would make the perfect outfit"</p>\n\n<p>However, the survey shows that 46% of people in Britain don&#8217;t like men wearing red trousers. Where do you stand?</p>\n\n<p></p>', 'Seeing Red', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'seeing-red', '', '', '2013-08-02 08:16:15', '2013-08-02 15:16:15', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/57160583926', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(827, 2, '2013-05-30 07:26:00', '2013-05-30 14:26:00', '<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/ce0e639d0ed9fe51af9208815ce222fa/tumblr_inline_mnm7yegh8P1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>No one dad is the same, fact. However, dad&#8217;s all around the world have been classified into different categories for those times when the big man deserves a gift.</p>\n<p>In this week&#8217;s gift guide, we take a close look at what would make 3 types of dad&#8217;s would revel in joy.</p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/1709a52b71bac12a167978bb85a7d0b8/tumblr_inline_mnm8273wPL1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p></p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/4d720fe8e4fca467bf9ac731d5f125d1/tumblr_inline_mnm82zZiJy1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p></p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/ea97bfda9de6be87f2ffd96ffe0d1371/tumblr_inline_mnm838oHdu1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n<p>___________________________________________________________________</p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/763bc8a626f9649ec410a65b7b74d57d/tumblr_inline_mnmce5DNG41qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>For the ultimate gift one can give any father - an Enclothed box.</p>\n<p>Simply request an invitation for him to join the Enclothed club at <a href="http://www.enclothed.co.uk">www.enclothed.co.uk</a> and have a box filled with great clothes chosen especially for him appear on his doorstep this fathers day.</p>', 'GIFT GUIDE: Father\'s Day', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gift-guide-fathers-day', '', '', '2013-05-30 07:26:00', '2013-05-30 14:26:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/51725068750', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(828, 2, '2013-05-29 08:26:27', '2013-05-29 15:26:27', '<div class="figure"><figure>\n  <img src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/50c14adc3907bf8477076c3197b551a6/tumblr_mnkg83MQJ21s2pu68o1_1280.jpg" alt="">\n</figure></div>\n\n    <p>#streetstyle #fashion #mensstyle</p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'streetstyle-fashion-mensstyle', '', '', '2013-05-29 08:26:27', '2013-05-29 15:26:27', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/51646570045', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(829, 2, '2013-05-24 06:33:41', '2013-05-24 13:33:41', '<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/8cf1c546559e31234ff112f6b24f84d6/tumblr_inline_mnb1f8JzoR1qz4rgp.jpg"/></p>\n\n<p>The Enclothed box, also known as Enbox, had a great time at Joe and the Juice today.</p>\n\n<p></p>', 'Enbox at Joe and the Juice', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'enbox-at-joe-and-the-juice', '', '', '2013-05-24 06:33:41', '2013-05-24 13:33:41', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/51223237623', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(830, 2, '2013-05-24 06:12:22', '2013-05-24 13:12:22', '<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/1a577475a8b895b348f39838c633075f/tumblr_inline_mnb0hsZmbE1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>With the BMW PGA championship this weekend, our personal stylists take a look at what to wear as a spectator.</p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/9340773f699bf5dc639b23c17b9f4cdb/tumblr_inline_mnb0ju3MtR1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>Golf courses cover a lot of ground, meaning there will be a lot of walking, coupled with standing around in complete silence whilst a shot is taken. With all this standing and walking, you will definitely want comfortable shoes. Golf shoes are designed with spikes, providing traction for powerful swings. However, as a spectator, leave the spikes to the players. There are more comfortable and stylish alternatives.</p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/276eaa1524106d2dab86edb0d875ba48/tumblr_inline_mnb0kwYNu11qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>Without a doubt, a polo top is essential at a golf touranment. However, you can still stand out from the crowd with what you wear on top - let’s face it, we need something to keep us warm in the UK.</p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/078e9c801c5b86ecf2329ded8114fb33/tumblr_inline_mnb0me50YG1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/53658d4163d055958aaf35c483255a9b/tumblr_inline_mnb0mtdAW71qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>As a rule of thumb - denim does not belong on the golf course. Chinos are a natural fit on a golf course, as are cords. Opt for a smart pair of shorts if it’s sunny.</p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/66658a74ef4be0f47578b8543c6e55ad/tumblr_inline_mnb0nfg7qr1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p></p>', 'WHAT TO WEAR: TO WATCH THE GOLF', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-to-wear-to-watch-the-golf', '', '', '2013-05-24 06:12:22', '2013-05-24 13:12:22', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/51222331460', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(831, 2, '2013-04-08 09:26:01', '2013-04-08 16:26:01', '<p class="MsoNormal"><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/ca3f86466e9c2ce597d5f1c12c3f22b4/tumblr_inline_mky2seTjkL1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span>The bomber jacket, A.K.A the G-1, is best known for its military standing. So who could have pictured the lightweight, tailored bomber jacket teamed with a preppy shirt or jeans and a t-shirt would look so good? Similar to the varsity jacket, the bomber is a must-have for spring with its ability to keep you looking sharp from day to night.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span> </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span> </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span>Here are some of our favourites:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/ffb388e7570502925df9b4b6ff579ee3/tumblr_inline_mky2pgJFyS1qz4rgp.png"/></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span>Wearing a sporty bomber with coloured chinos gives this outfit an element of laid-back sophistication</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span> </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/f04b7c36958d9ef88a69657c36d37d19/tumblr_inline_mky2v7CBHp1qz4rgp.png"/></span></p>\n\n<p>For the man who&#8217;s not afraid to wear peach. This is a great outfit to wear to the office on a Friday</p>\n\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/d47307f775dc98dc603fde9653706fa1/tumblr_inline_mky2wadHeQ1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>For the less adventurous - This is a relaxed and casual attire.</p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/0286ddd183058dcf924d2103c499d053/tumblr_inline_mky2xfailJ1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n<p>For a pop of colour on a sunny day - wearing pale neutrals with one bright piece will definitely get you noticed.</p>\n\n<p><!--EndFragment--></p>', 'A look at the Bomber Jacket', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'a-look-at-the-bomber-jacket', '', '', '2013-04-08 09:26:01', '2013-04-08 16:26:01', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/47463251751', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(832, 2, '2013-03-12 08:23:37', '2013-03-12 15:23:37', '<div class="figure"><figure>\n  <img src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/18701e72c73ad4f52fe254c69f721ea0/tumblr_mjk03diW6u1s2pu68o1_1280.jpg" alt="">\n</figure></div>\n\n    <p>Inject some colour this spring even if its just your shoes! #shoes #mensstyle #style #menswear</p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'inject-some-colour-this-spring-even-if-its-just-your-shoes-shoes-mensstyle-style-menswear', '', '', '2013-03-12 08:23:37', '2013-03-12 15:23:37', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/45191897456', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(833, 2, '2013-02-15 06:16:00', '2013-02-15 14:16:00', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span>Here in the UK, we are no strangers to puddles, downpours and “light rain” in between sunny spells.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span>The brogue is an innovation made by us Brits, whereby shoemakers poke holes as a way to drain surplus water. Brogues were traditionally known for their outdoor, country characteristics, never seen in more formal circumstances.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span>The modern brogue however is built less for weatherproofing, more for business and smart/casual attire. </span><span>So where does that leave us Brits with wet feet? Wellington’s won’t be appreciated in the office.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span> </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span>We caught up with SWIMS at the Jacket Required event, who explained that waterproofing your feet doesn’t have to reside in the countryside.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/9a8707441d49c7a96c9cef97aa275f68/tumblr_inline_mi9nvgFGGh1qz4rgp.png"/></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/8964bf863f173c528946e42b5e6d45c1/tumblr_inline_mi9m9lunRG1qz4rgp.png"/></span></p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/0fe6ddeb1d599aaabb4999a98fd809a6/tumblr_inline_mi9m9wqh8f1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/1bd72607175a7c707bfc5f164c0708e0/tumblr_inline_mi9majhoNj1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/795d92e73d457aa31b8aec6657e8a8f4/tumblr_inline_mi9nmtqdhd1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p></p>', 'Weatherproofing our Feet', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'weatherproofing-our-feet', '', '', '2013-02-15 06:16:00', '2013-02-15 14:16:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/43147510165', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(834, 2, '2013-02-12 07:29:37', '2013-02-12 15:29:37', '<div class="figure"><figure>\n  <img src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/7e3687aa53d8ff872c19605f38f97a5a/tumblr_mi45pd6pBU1s2pu68o1_1280.jpg" alt="">\n</figure></div>\n\n    <p>It&#8217;s still cold enough for us to be grateful for stocking up on cashmere scarfs from Johnston of Elgin #menswear #style #fashion</p>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'it8217s-still-cold-enough-for-us-to-be-grateful-for-stocking-up-on-cashmere-scarfs-from-johnston-of-elgin-menswear-style-fashion', '', '', '2013-02-12 07:29:37', '2013-02-12 15:29:37', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/42927178644', 0, 'post', '', 0),
